OL,4,CBacklash as 'pinged' staff rules called
OL,5,Cunworkable
OL,6, Industry bodies have reacted with
OL,7, dismay at the government's plan for
OL,8, firms to apply for staff to be exempt
OL,9, from coronavirus self-isolation rules.
OL,11,FThe government has said there will be
OL,12,Fno list of critical workers exempt from
OL,13,Fisolating rules and exemptions will be
OL,14,F"considered on a case-by-case basis".
OL,16,FKaren Dee, chief executive of the
OL,17,Fairport operators association, said the
OL,18,Fscheme was "simply unworkable".
OL,20,FThe food supply industry called for
OL,21,Fclarity on how the scheme would work.
